### Security
- All authenticated routes wrapped in `ProtectedRoute` component — redirect to `/sign-in` if no session
- Supabase Row-Level Security (RLS) on all user data tables — users can only read/write their own rows
- Beta tier gating enforced at RLS level via `user_tier` field in `profiles` table — not just frontend routing
- Claude API key stored as Supabase secret / environment variable — never exposed to client
- Stripe webhook signature verification on all payment events (post-beta)

### Cost Estimate (Beta — 10 users)
- Supabase: Free tier sufficient for 10 users
- Anthropic Claude API: ~$0.005/1K tokens; ~50-100 report generations at ~10K tokens each = ~$5-10 total for beta
- N8N: Self-hosted or cloud free tier
- Total beta infrastructure cost: <$50/month

