### Key Relationships
- One user → many assessments (retakes allowed)
- AE Ladder assessment → calibrates MRA assessment (stage-specific scoring)
- MRA assessment → feeds Quarter Map (3P tags, capability scores)
- Quarter Map → generates Capability Cards (one per selected capability area)
- Capability Cards → contain Initiatives → contain Milestones
- Milestone completion → triggers maturity score recalculation on MRA
- Locked Quarter Map → generates Sprint → generates Sprint Launch Document

