### FR-009 — Capability Cards and Initiative/Milestone Builder
**Priority:** P0 | **Feature:** Pro Suite — Sprint Planning | **Build Status:** Built — verify/design-align

**Execution Hierarchy (ArchitectOS does not go below milestone level):**
